== Example of the brofist ==
Here's how you make a brofist, first you take a middle finger ASCII...

'''MIDDLE FINGER:'''<br/>
........................./´¯/)<br/>
......................,/¯..//<br/>
...................../..../ /<br/>
............./´¯/'...'/´¯¯`·¸<br/>
........../'/.../..../......./¨¯\<br/>
........('(...´(..´......,~/'...')<br/>
.........\.................\/..../<br/>
..........''...\.......... _.·´<br/>
............\..............(<br/>
..............\.............\<br/>
<br/>
Then get rid of the first three lines and add a ...................__ above the fist <br/>

'''BROFIST:'''<br/>
...................__<br/>
............./´¯/'...'/´¯¯`·¸<br/>
........../'/.../..../......./¨¯\<br/>
........('(...´...´.... ¯~/'...')<br/>
.........\.................'...../<br/>
..........''...\.......... _.·´<br/>
............\..............( <br/>
<br/>
And there you have the bird call to the [[basement dwellers]] at /v/!



